            <requirements value="This code SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @codeSystem=&quot;2.16.840.1.113883.5.6&quot; (CodeSystem: HL7ActClass urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.5.6) (CONF:1198-32154)."/>
